{"tid":313313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［一圖］［冇證冇據］警車疑隨街閃燈 逼前方私家車開快啲","createTime":"2017-07-08T08:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T08:33:48.000Z","uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"790290faaad38a38d7d95af090d5bd8dc761d403","tid":313313,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"警車疑隨街閃燈 逼前方私家車開快啲<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/162130_4d55437a116294f93055b4ba23a26367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F162130_4d55437a116294f93055b4ba23a26367.jpg&h=8b3bcaec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影唔到開警車燈一刻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架警車見前面塞車就突然開著車頂閃燈 扮尻哂趕時間想逼前面車行快啲<br />\n之後臨到佢果架就轉紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n警犬就死死地氣停翻係到熄翻車頂閃燈<br />\n而如果我冇聽錯的話係警車熄燈前一刻 路面突然有兩次響安聲。<br />\n疑為警車發爛渣而響。<br />\n利申：響安非確定為警車發出。"},{"pid":"47c6af944667f3e3d85c47d323d33a1fb02f5887","tid":313313,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警車疑隨街閃燈 逼前方私家車開快啲<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/162130_4d55437a116294f93055b4ba23a26367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F162130_4d55437a116294f93055b4ba23a26367.jpg&h=8b3bcaec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影唔到開警車燈一刻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架警車見前面塞車就突然開著車頂閃燈 扮尻哂趕時間想逼前面車行快啲<br />\n之後臨到佢果架就轉紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n警犬就死死地氣停翻係到熄翻車頂閃燈<br />\n而如果我冇聽錯的話係警車熄燈前一刻 路面突然有兩次響安聲。<br />\n疑為警車發爛渣而響。<br />\n利申：響安非確定為警車發出。</blockquote><br />\n屌你老味又開錯台"}]}